rama-dharma, or man\xc3\x95s steppingstone for spiritual understanding. Human civilization begins from the stage of var\xe2\x80\x9a\xe2\x88\x92\xe2\x80\x9crama-dharma, or specific duties in terms of the specific \nmodes of nature of the body obtained. Discharging one\xc3\x95s specific duty in any field of action in accordance with var\xe2\x80\x9a\xe2\x88\x92\xe2\x80\x9crama-dharma serves to elevate one to a higher status of life.
