b'devotee in K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa consciousness, although far away from the Lord\xc3\x95s abode, can elevate himself to that abode simply by thinking of Him constantly\xc3\x91by engagement in K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa consciousness. He does not feel the pangs of material miseries; this state of life is called brahma-nirv\xe2\x88\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa, or the absence of material miseries due to being constantly immersed in the Supreme.
