b'na dhana\xe2\x80\xb9 na jana\xe2\x80\xb9 na sundar\xe2\x80\x9d\xe2\x80\xb9 kavit\xe2\x88\x92\xe2\x80\xb9 v\xe2\x88\x92 jagad\xe2\x80\x9d\xe2\x80\x9ca k\xe2\x88\x92maye.mama janmani janman\xe2\x80\x9d\xe2\x80\x9cvare bhavat\xe2\x88\x92d bhaktir ahaituk\xe2\x80\x9d tvayi."O Almighty Lord, I have no desire to accumulate wealth, nor to enjoy beautiful women. Nor do I want any number of followers. What I want only is the causeless mercy of Your devotional service in my life, birth after birth."
