PURPORTA K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa conscious yog\xe2\x80\x9d is the perfect seer because he sees K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa, the Supreme, situated in everyone\xc3\x95s heart as Supersoul (Param\xe2\x88\x92tm\xe2\x88\x92). \xe2\x80\xa6\xe2\x80\x9cvara\xc5\xa1 The Lord in His Param\xe2\x88\x92tm\xe2\x88\x92 feature is situated within both the heart of the dog and that of a br\xe2\x88\x92hma\xe2\x80\x9aa. The perfect yog\xe2\x80\x9d knows that the Lord is eternally transcendental and is not materially \naffected by His presence in either a dog or a br\xe2\x88\x92hma\xe2\x80\x9aa. That is the supreme neutrality of the Lord. The individual soul is also situated in the individual heart, but he is not present in all hearts. That is the distinction between the individual soul and the Supersoul. One who is not factually in the practice of \nyoga cannot see so clearly. A K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa conscious person can see K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa in the heart of both the believer and nonbeliever. In the sm\xe2\x80\x9eti this is confirmed as follows: \xe2\x88\x92tatatv\xe2\x88\x92c ca m\xe2\x88\x92t\xe2\x80\x9etv\xe2\x88\x92d \xe2\x88\x92tm\xe2\x88\x92 hi paramo hari\xc5\xa1.The Lord, being the source of all beings, is like the mother and the maintainer. As the mother is neutral to all different kinds of children, the Supreme Father (or Mother) is also. Consequently the Supersoul is always in every living being. Outwardly, also, every living being is situated in the energy of the Lord. As \nwill be explained in the Seventh Chapter, the Lord has, primarily, two energies!the spiritual (or superior) and the material (or inferior). The living entity, although part of the superior energy, is conditioned by the inferior energy; the living entity is always in the Lord\xc3\x95s energy. Every living entity is situated in Him in one way or another. The yog\xe2\x80\x9d sees equally because he sees '
b'that all living entities, although in different situations according to the results of fruitive work, in all circumstances remain the servants of God. While in the material energy, the living entity serves the material senses; and while in spiritual energy, he serves the Supreme Lord directly. In either case the living entity is the servant of God. This vision of equality is perfect in a person in K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa consciousness.
