ctice. This very understanding that K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa is present as Param\xe2\x88\x92tm\xe2\x88\x92 in everyone\xc3\x95s heart \nmakes the yog\xe2\x80\x9d faultless. The Vedas confirm this inconceivable potency of the Lord as follows:eko \xc3\x95pi san bahudh\xe2\x88\x92 yo \xc3\x95vabh\xe2\x88\x92ti'
