b'unto the leaves of a tree, and the main tree is likened to K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa. K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa, dwelling in Goloka V\xe2\x80\x9end\xe2\x88\x92vana, His supreme abode, systematically conducts all affairs of both universes (material and spiritual) without a flaw by power of His all-pervasiveness.
