e should know that our protection \nmust be a living force. Thus K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa is the supreme living entity. Since K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa is the source of our generation, or the supreme father, no one can be a better friend than K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa, nor can anyone be a better well-wisher. K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa is the original source of creation and the ultimate rest after annihilation. K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa is therefore the eternal cause of all causes.'
