TRANSLATION
He who knows in truth this glory and power of Mine engages in unalloyed devotional service; of this there is no doubt.
PURPORTThe highest summit of spiritual perfection is knowledge of the Supreme Personality of Godhead. Unless one is firmly convinced of the different opulences of the Supreme Lord, he cannot engage in devotional service. Generally people know that God is great, but they do not know in detail how God is great. Here are the details. If one knows factually how God is great, then naturally he becomes a surrendered soul and engages himself in the devotional service of the Lord. When one factually knows the opulences of the Supreme, there is no alternative but to surrender to Him. This factual knowledge can be known from the descriptions in \xe2\x80\xa1r\xe2\x80\x9dmad-Bh\xe2\x88\x92gavatam and \nBhagavad-g\xe2\x80\x9dt\xe2\x88\x92 and similar literatures.In the administration of this universe there are many demigods distributed throughout the planetary system, and the chief of them are Brahm\xe2\x88\x92, Lord \xe2\x80\xa1iva and the four great Kum\xe2\x88\x92ras and other patriarchs. There are many forefathers of the population of the universe, and all of them are born of the Supreme Lord K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa. The Supreme Personality of Godhead, K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa, is the original forefather of all forefathers.\nThese are some of the opulences of the Supreme Lord. When one is firmly convinced of them, he accepts K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa with great faith and without any doubt, and he engages in devotional service. All this particular knowledge is required in order to increase one\xc3\x95s interest in the loving devotional service of the Lord. One should not neglect to understand fully how great K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa is, for by knowing the greatness of K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa one will be able to be fixed in sincere devotional service.
