b'aha\xe2\x80\xb9 sarvasya prabhavomatta\xc5\xa1 sarva\xe2\x80\xb9 pravartateiti matv\xe2\x88\x92 bhajante m\xe2\x88\x92\xe2\x80\xb9budh\xe2\x88\x92 bh\xe2\x88\x92va-samanvit\xe2\x88\x92\xc5\xa1aham\xc3\x91I; sarvasya\xc3\x91of all; prabhava\xc5\xa1\xc3\x91source of generation; matta\xc5\xa1\xc3\x91from Me; sarvam\xc3\x91everything; pravartate\xc3\x91emanates; iti\xc3\x91thus; matv\xe2\x88\x92\xc3\x91knowing; bhajante\xc3\x91becomes devoted; m\xe2\x88\x92m\xc3\x91unto Me; budh\xe2\x88\x92\xc5\xa1\xc3\x91learned; bh\xe2\x88\x92va-samanvit\xe2\x88\x92\xc5\xa1\xc3\x91with great attention.
