b'understand the totality of K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa\xc3\x95s affairs. Still the devotees try to understand K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa, but not on the principle that they will be able to understand K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa fully at any specific time or in any state of life. Rather, the very topics of K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa are so relishable that they appear to them as nectar. Thus they enjoy them. In discussing K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa\xc3\x95s opulences and His diverse energies, the pure devotees take transcendental pleasure. Therefore they want to hear and discuss them. K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa knows that living entities do not understand the extent of His opulences; He therefore agrees to state only the principal manifestations \nof His different energies. The word pr\xe2\x88\x92dh\xe2\x88\x92nyata\xc5\xa1 (principal) is very important because we can understand only a few of the principal details of the Supreme Lord, for His features are unlimited. It is not possible to understand them all. And as used in this verse, refers to the opulences by which He controls the whole manifestation. In the Amara-ko\xe2\x80\x9ca dictionary it is stated that indicates an exceptional opulence.The impersonalist or the pantheist cannot understand the exceptional \nopulences of the Supreme Lord nor the manifestations of His divine energy. Both in the material world and in the spiritual world His energies are distributed in every variety of manifestation. Now K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa is describing what can be directly perceived by the common man; thus part of His variegated energy is described in this way.
