\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9drodaka\xe2\x80\x9c\xe2\x88\x92y\xe2\x80\x9d Vi\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9au, in this material manifestation.\xc3\x93 The Supreme Lord K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa, the cause of \nall causes, lies down in the cosmic ocean as Mah\xe2\x88\x92-Vi\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9au or K\xe2\x88\x92ra\xe2\x80\x9aodaka\xe2\x80\x9c\xe2\x88\x92y\xe2\x80\x9d Vi\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9au, and therefore K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa is the beginning of this universe, the maintainer of the universal manifestation, and the end of all the energy.'
