Of horses know Me to be Uccai\xc5\xa1\xe2\x80\x9crav\xe2\x88\x92, who rose out of the ocean, born of the elixir of immortality; of lordly elephants I am Air\xe2\x88\x92vata, and among men I am \nthe monarch.
