nterested to understand the Supreme Personality of Godhead, K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa, and who follow in the footsteps of Arjuna should understand that K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa not only theoretically presented Himself as the Supreme, but actually revealed Himself as the Supreme.The Lord gave Arjuna the necessary power to see His universal form because He knew that Arjuna did not particularly want to see it, as we have already \nexplained.
