PURPORTIt may be that one is unable to even sympathize with the activities of K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa consciousness because of social, familial or religious considerations or because of some other impediments. If one attaches himself directly to the activities of K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa consciousness, there may be objection from family members, or so many other difficulties. For one who has such a problem, it is advised that he \nsacrifice the accumulated result of his activities to some good cause. Such procedures are described in the Vedic rules. There are many descriptions of sacrifices and special functions of the pumundi or special work in which the result of one\xc3\x95s previous action may be applied. Thus one may gradually become elevated to the state of knowledge. It is also found that when one who is not even interested in the activities of K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa consciousness gives charity to some hospital or some other social institution, he gives up the hard-earned results of \nhis activities. That is also recommended here because by the practice of giving up the fruits of one\xc3\x95s activities one is sure to purify his mind gradually, and in that purified stage of mind one becomes able to understand K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa '
b'consciousness. Of course K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa consciousness is not dependant on any other experience because K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa consciousness itself can purify one\xc3\x95s mind, but if there are impediments to K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa consciousness, one may try to give up the result of his action. In that respect, social service, community service, national service, sacrifice for one\xc3\x95s country, etc., may be accepted so that some day one may come to the stage of pure devotional service to the Supreme Lord. In Bhagavad-g\xe2\x80\x9dt\xe2\x88\x92 we find it is stated: If one decides to sacrifice for the supreme cause, even if he does not know that the supreme \ncause is K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa, he will come gradually to understand that K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa is the supreme cause by the sacrificial method.
