TRANSLATION
One who is not envious but who is a kind friend to all living entities, who does not think himself a proprietor, who is free from false ego and equal both in \nhappiness and distress, who is always satisfied and engaged in devotional service \nwith determination and whose mind and intelligence are in agreement with Me\xc3\x91he is very dear to Me.'
