tion. That Supreme Personality also has a localized aspect as Param\xe2\x88\x92tm\xe2\x88\x92. By incarnating Himself as the son of Satyavat\xe2\x80\x9d and Par\xe2\x88\x92\xe2\x80\x9cara, He explains the Vedic knowledge as Vy\xe2\x88\x92sadeva.'
